    <note type="biography">
        <p>Danish physician and malacologist. Head doctor, Copenhagen hospital, 1866–1905. As a malacologist, worked mainly on gastropod systematics. Worked on the mollusc collections of several expeditions including the <hi rend="italic">Challenger</hi> and the German expedition to the Philippine archipelago.</p></note>
